analysts, who had expected a slowdown due to the resurgence
of the Swiss franc.
</LP>
<TEXT>
   The measure of wholesale import prices rose 0.1% month to
month in April and declined 1.3% from April 1989, while the
gauge of domestic wholesale prices rose 0.2% from March and
increased 2.6% from last April.
